1
00:00:43,780 --> 00:00:46,780
=Strange Tales of Jiangcheng=
=Episode 10=

2
00:00:47,470 --> 00:00:48,990
Today, the feud between Qin Weilian and me

3
00:00:48,990 --> 00:00:50,160
