I'm here. Come on.

10
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:02,200
How do you want to settle it?

11
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:03,360
I won't resist.

12
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:04,360
Lawyer Qin.

13
00:01:04,470 --> 00:01:05,310
Captain Song.

14
00:01:06,440 --> 00:01:07,440
This is between

15
