Miss Jiangyun and me.

16
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,240
Please don't get involved.

17
00:01:13,470 --> 00:01:14,410
You're a good girl.

18
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:16,560
I know we've come down to this

19
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:18,970
for many reasons.

20
00:01:19,750 --> 00:01:20,590
And I also know

21
00:01:21,270 --> 00:01:23,200
you will release Huole and Xiaofan,
right?

22
00:01:23,550 --> 00:01:24,410
Shut up!

23
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,080
Qin Weilian.

24
00:01:27,110 --> 00:01:28,360
I want you to watch

25
