your son die in front of you.

26
00:01:34,550 --> 00:01:35,960
No!

27
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,610
Director Xu, quickly find someone

28
00:01:37,830 --> 00:01:39,490
to save them.

29
00:01:45,870 --> 00:01:46,710
Someone!

30
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:50,640
Song He.

31
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:52,800
We're here!

32
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,200
Dad, we're here!

33
00:01:54,890 --> 00:01:55,950
Over there!

34
