41
00:02:10,310 --> 00:02:11,150
Let me think about it.

42
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,200
In detective novels,

43
00:02:22,550 --> 00:02:24,170
most secret rooms are set underground.

44
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:25,920
Trying to trap people in an attic,

45
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:27,640
isn't that nonsense?

46
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:39,730
Miss Jiangyun.

47
00:02:42,150 --> 00:02:43,080
My life

48
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:45,520
is too bitter.

49
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:47,040
Take her away.

50
00:02:59,300 --> 00:03:02,260
(One month later)

51
00:03:02,420 --> 00:03:06,820
(Where should one dwell?
How should one subdue the mind?)

52
00:03:06,830 --> 00:03:08,450
The judicial trial is unchangeable.

53
