232
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,520
your achievements,

233
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:37,790
and then we'll know

234
00:11:37,790 --> 00:11:38,840
where to put it.

235
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,680
How about that?

236
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:40,600
Deal.

237
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:42,510
Deal.

238
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,080
Captain Song.

239
00:11:45,670 --> 00:11:46,790
I joined the police station

240
00:11:46,790 --> 00:11:48,850
to become a good police officer
who seeks the truth.

241
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,200
In this regard,

242
00:11:50,270 --> 00:11:51,190
