Dad.

248
00:12:44,550 --> 00:12:45,390
Why are you here?

249
00:12:45,520 --> 00:12:46,790
Just passing by after work.

250
00:12:46,790 --> 00:12:47,630
By the way,

251
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:49,360
who were you chatting with just now?

252
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:52,690
Mr. Che Jingwen
from Sicun Middle School.

253
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,320
Is he your friend?

254
00:12:55,190 --> 00:12:56,430
Mr. Che doesn't make friends.

255
00:12:56,430 --> 00:12:57,360
He came to see me

256
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,930
specifically for Jushangfang.

257
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:01,090
He thinks Jushangfang is a good place

258
00:13:01,550 --> 00:13:02,930
and shouldn't just disappear.

259
00:13:03,430 --> 00:13:05,400
We should find a capable person

260
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:06,810
to reopen it.

261
00:13:09,400 --> 00:13:11,210
Mr. Che makes a good point.

262
00:13:12,070 --> 00:13:12,910
But

263
00:13:13,790 --> 00:13:15,360
where can we find

264
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,240
another Su Jiangyun in your heart?

265
00:13:18,670 --> 00:13:19,850
- You...
- Just kidding, Dad.

266
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:20,960
Just kidding.

267
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:22,000
Slick.

268
00:13:23,070 --> 00:13:24,590
Was there nothing else

269
00:13:24,590 --> 00:13:25,720
Mr. Che wanted to discuss with you?

270
00:13:26,430 --> 00:13:27,270
He...

271
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:29,880
You kid.

272
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:31,490
You speak more and more like a police officer.

273
00:13:31,760 --> 00:13:33,190
Are you questioning me like a criminal?

274
00:13:33,190 --> 00:13:34,930
No, I'm just curious.

275
00:13:36,270 --> 00:13:37,120
Let's go home.

276
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:39,680
Walk properly.

277
00:13:40,310 --> 00:13:41,690
Don't put your arm around my shoulders.

278
00:14:25,190 --> 00:14:26,760
(Could it be some treasure?)

279
00:14:52,030 --> 00:14:52,870
Help!

280
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:54,970
Help!

